<strong>Avós Paternos:</strong> <a href="{% link _pessoas/SchererFredericoJacobTheobaldo1885.md %}">Frederico Jacob Theobaldo Scherer (1885-1948)</a> e <a href="{% link _pessoas/SchererIdalinaRenaldina1890.md %}">Idalina Renaldina Scherer (1890-1973)</a> <a href="#refs" class="ref">[1]</a><br />
<strong>Avós Maternos:</strong> <a href="" class="underconstruction">João Henrique Quinot (1892-1968)</a> e <a href="" class="underconstruction">Leopoldina Mayer (1894-????)</a> <a href="#refs" class="ref">[1]</a><br />
